yle=3D"line-height: 1.4285715;"><code>DOMDocument</code>.</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"TheXmlTextFieldType-Validation"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);=
">Validation</span></h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Validation of the internal format is =
performed in the&nbsp;<strong><code>eZ\Publish\Core\FieldType\XmlText\Input=
\EzXml</code></strong>&nbsp;class.</span></p>
<h2 id=3D"TheXmlTextFieldType-Settings">Settings</h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Following settings are available:</sp=
an></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Name</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
