<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><code><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">n=
umRows</span></code></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>int</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>10</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Defines the number of rows for the online editor=
 in the administration interface.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><code><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,51,102);">t=
agPreset</span></code></p></td>
