<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>Type::TAG_PRESET_DEFAULT</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span>Preset of tags for the online editor in=
 the administration interface.</span></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
